response.overview: This expansive documentary tracks the career of Florida-born producer-singer-rapper T-Pain from his early solo work to his eventual success on the international rap scene, including his collaborations with Bow Wow, R. Kelly, Kanye West and others. T-Pain pushes the boundaries of rap with his innovative echo-like vocals, and the Grammy winning artist's long list of collaborators reads like a Who's Who of the rap world.
response.title: T-Pain: Digital Collaborations
